
  Responsible for day to day operations and management of a dormitory   
  Handle allocation of unit, check-in and check-out   
  Ensure full compliance to operation controls, SOPs, policies, procedure, service standards &amp; all government authorities’ requirements
  Ensure that the dormitory premises are satisfactorily clean and rooms are equipped accordingly for residents
  Overall responsible for the management of the dormitory and efficient management of manpower and resources 
  To undertake any other duties as assigned by the Supervisor.
